</p> <p>The positive economic</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170189775/image_2170189775.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742540-financials-are-leveraged-for-soft-landing", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 10:35:00"}, {"id": "4742534", "title": "Lululemon Q3 2024 Earnings Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lululemon building exterior with woman entering store by sign\" data-id=\"824053452\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">ablokhin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>While the overall market continues to hit All-time High almost every other day, Lulu (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LULU\" title=\"Lululemon Athletica Inc.\">LULU</a>) has been battling the skeptics for much of this year. There is still a long way to go, but with the stock now up almost</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742534-lululemon-q3-2024-earnings-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 10:03:00"}, {"id": "4742533", "title": "How To Make Sense Of Emerging Market Debt In A Global Portfolio", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Emerging Markets\" data-id=\"1296098015\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4592px\" height=\"3061px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">tum3123</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Damien Buchet, CFA, Chief investment officer, Principal Finisterre</em></p> <p>Emerging market debt (EMD) has garnered increasing attention from investors for many years. While the asset class has historically delivered attractive, diversified returns driven by high income generation, many investors still need help understanding</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742533-how-to-make-sense-of-emerging-market-debt-in-global-portfolio", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 09:55:00"}, {"id": "4742528", "title": "McDonald's: Investors Will Get A Lot Of Stomach Pain Here", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/2148328625/photo/mcdonalds-in-times-square-with-a-crowd-of-people-in-manhattan-in-new-york-city.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=8ockJiN-9yM2xFW0-xqlGQv3brwjAfyy31WdeyFnuLc=\" alt='McDonald\"s in Times Square with a crowd of people in Manhattan in New York City' data-id=\"2148328625\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Jay Mize/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It's been a great year for U.S. stocks, but one of America's most iconic global brands has not been a participant in this year's rally. McDonald's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MCD\" title=\"McDonald's Corporation\">MCD</a></span>), the quintessential purveyor of Big Macs</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742528-mcdonalds-stock-investors-rising-labor-costs-operating-margin-decline-sell", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 09:31:02"}, {"id": "4742527", "title": "Tradeweb Government Bond Update - November 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Government bonds memo inscription on the page with calculation.\" data-id=\"1282660847\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5600px\" height=\"3733px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">designer491</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Apart from Japan, global government debt markets reversed October\u2019s sell-off in November, with the five biggest movers all in Europe. The month also saw weak economic data published in the Euro area, starting with the HCOB Flash Eurozone Manufacturing PMI, which dropped to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742527-tradeweb-government-bond-update-november-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 08:15:00"}, {"id": "4740936", "title": "Politics And The Markets 12/06/24", "description": "<p><span>This is the forum for daily political discussion on Seeking Alpha. A new version is published every market day.</span></p> <p>Please don't leave political comments on other articles or posts on the site.</p> <p>The comments below are not regulated with the same rigor as the rest of the site, and this is an <strong>'enter at your own risk' </strong>area as discussion can get very heated. If you can't stand the heat... you know what they say...</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>More on Today's Markets:</span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Moderation Guidelines:</b></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><span></span></b>We remove comments under the following categories:</p> <ul> <li>Personal attacks on another user account</li> <li>Anti-Vaxxer or covid related misinformation</li> <li>Stereotyping, prejudiced or racist language about individuals or the topic under discussion.</li> <li>Inciting violence messages, encouraging hate groups and political violence.</li> </ul> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regardless of which side of the political divide you find yourself, please be courteous and don't direct abuse at other users.</p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">For any issue with regards to comments please email us at : moderation@seekingalpha.com.</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>Seeking Alpha's Disclosure:</span></b><span> Past performance is no guarantee of future results. No recommendation or advice is being given as to whether any investment is suitable for a particular investor. Any views or opinions expressed above may not reflect those of Seeking Alpha as a whole. Seeking Alpha is not a licensed securities dealer, broker or US investment adviser or investment bank. Our analysts are third party authors that include both professional investors and individual investors who may not be licensed or certified by any institute or regulatory body.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"> </p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <div class=\"sa-art article-width paywall-full-content\" id=\"a-body\"><span class=\"content-end p p1\"></span></div>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740936-politics-and-the-markets-120624", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 08:00:00"}, {"id": "4742522", "title": "SVIX: All Quiet On The Western Front", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A group of pens and pencils arranged as a graph\" data-id=\"2159569962\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>Akin the namesake movie, volatility can take sudden turns with the advent of an economic or political event. The introduction of ETFs catered towards this asset class has allowed investors to take a view on market</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742522-svix-etf-sell-given-current-vix-levels", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 07:55:42"}, {"id": "4742519", "title": "Employers Holdings Has Room To Grow", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Finance background\" data-id=\"625756386\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" siz