/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Hispanolistic</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Two years after the launch of ChatGPT by OpenAI, the artificial intelligence theme continues to make headlines, and for those still wondering whether it is still time to invest, it depends on the area of the AI ecosystem being targeted, one of which</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742518-dtcr-etf-data-centers-digital-infrastructure-for-ai-exposure", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 07:28:10"}, {"id": "4742517", "title": "Dollarama Q3: The Veneer Loses Some Of Its Shine, Management Comments Offer Hints", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dollar sign blowing away\" data-id=\"1142952057\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"9452px\" height=\"5289px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=